            "heading": "Care Instructions",
            "icon": "heart",
            "content": "<p>To care for your sustainable organic clothing, wash in cold water with mild detergent. Avoid bleach and harsh chemicals. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry. Handle recycled fabrics gently. By caring for your clothing thoughtfully, you extend its lifespan and reduce environmental impact.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
